<section class="page hv-about-page">
  {% render 'breadcrumbs', page: page %}
  <div class="panel hv-policy hv-about">
    <p class="hv-about__badge">Collector-run · NZ based</p>
    <h1>{{ page.title | default: 'About HoloVault' }}</h1>

    <p>HoloVault is a small New Zealand based Pokémon TCG singles store built by a collector, for collectors.</p>
    <p>What started as a personal hobby quickly became a passion for finding great cards, helping others complete collections, and creating a store that feels honest, personal, and community focused.</p>
    <p>Every card listed is carefully sourced, checked, photographed, and packed with care. We focus on clean condition notes, fair pricing, and making the buying experience simple and enjoyable — whether you’re chasing grails, favourite Pokémon, modern hits, or unique language variants.</p>
    <p>At HoloVault, we know every order means something. Whether it’s your first single or the final card for your binder, we appreciate every collector who supports the store.</p>
    <p><strong>Thanks for being part of the journey 💜</strong></p>

    <div class="hv-about__grid">
      <div class="hv-about__card">
        <h2>What we sell</h2>
        <p>Individual singles across English, Japanese, and Chinese sets — sourced with collectors in mind.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="hv-about__card">
        <h2>How we pack</h2>
        <p>Sleeves, top loaders, team bags, and secure mailers — extra protection for higher-value cards.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="hv-about__card">
        <h2>Fair pricing</h2>
        <p>Collectr market data where applicable, updated regularly so you see current values in NZD.</p>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="hv-about__cta">
      <a class="btn primary" href="{% if collections.pokemon %}{{ collections.pokemon.url }}{% else %}{{ routes.all_products_collection_url }}{% endif %}">Browse singles</a>
      <a class="btn secondary" href="/pages/contact">Contact us</a>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

{% schema %}
{
  "name": "About page",
  "settings": []
}
{% endschema %}
